    "name": "Dodge Barrage",
    "steam_appid": 2201000,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<br><br>Dodge Barrage is a chaotic dodgeball party game. Use quick reflexes and aggressive plays to throw, dodge, and parry your way to victory. Play with up to four players either locally or online.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201000/extras/5ebe05196f3f5d97de346b4378e46d83.poster.avif?t=1724396607\" width=732 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201000/extras/5ebe05196f3f5d97de346b4378e46d83.webm?t=1724396607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201000/extras/5ebe05196f3f5d97de346b4378e46d83.mp4?t=1724396607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Inspired heavily by fighting games, every move in your kit has an equivalent counterattack. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Spike a ball from above to give your opponents less time to react.<br></li><li> Catch a ball out of the air to instantly refill your Special Meter.<br></li><li> Charge a throw to threaten the whole field and unleash a surefire attack.<br></li><li> Parry a throw in mid-air with your own throw.<br></li><li> Bounce a throw off the wall for a surprising mix-up.<br></li><li> Dash away from incoming attacks.<br></li><li> Tackle the ball out of your opponent’s hands. </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201000/extras/16c377bbf3eece2f976359705403532f.poster.avif?t=1724396607\" width=756 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201000/extras/16c377bbf3eece2f976359705403532f.webm?t=1724396607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201000/extras/16c377bbf3eece2f976359705403532f.mp4?t=1724396607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features </h2><br>- Team battles. Team up with your friends or fight head-to-head.<br><br>- Online and Local Multiplayer. Join up to 4 players in chaotic sports action. Built with rollback netcode.<br><br>- Arcade Mode. Play offline in a series of battles that ramp up in difficulty.<br><br>- 7 characters. From the ferocious Pam, to the timid Lewis, every character is dripping with personality.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201000/extras/f90300d0f79cc9539cee84b5317bcf82.gif?t=1724396607\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201000/extras/f90300d0f79cc9539cee84b5317bcf82.poster.avif?t=1724396607\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br><br>- 11 game modes: <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Time </strong>- Rack up the most points before time runs out.<br></li><li> <strong>Stamina </strong>- Adds HP bars to the game. Don’t let yourself get knocked out.<br></li><li> <strong>Points </strong>- First team to X points takes the win.<br></li><li> <strong>Crown </strong>- King of the Hill - hold the crown for a cumulative 2 minutes to win.<br></li><li> <strong>Rush Down </strong>- Tackle your opponents to earn points rather than hitting them with the ball.<br></li><li> <strong>Simplified </strong>- Removes special meters to help beginners master the basics.<br></li><li> <strong>Boundless </strong>- Disables out of bounds to enable a really in-your-face style of play.<br></li><li> <strong>Fully Charged </strong>- Special Meters are always full. Good luck dodging when every throw is charged.<br></li><li> <strong>Hot Potato </strong>- Balls respawn very quickly, which encourages more agressive play.<br></li><li> <strong>All the Balls </strong>- Adds 8 balls to the field. Good luck trying to dodge in a proper barrage.<br></li><li> <strong>Custom </strong>- Mix and match all the win conditions at once, including changing how points are scored.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201000/extras/8b6f425967be899ca2e914022ed7f39b.poster.avif?t=1724396607\" width=732 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201000/extras/8b6f425967be899ca2e914022ed7f39b.webm?t=1724396607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201000/extras/8b6f425967be899ca2e914022ed7f39b.mp4?t=1724396607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- 3 maps that change up your strategies.<br><br>- A Smorgasbord of Customization Options. Keep gameplay fresh with the ability to customize every aspect of not just the win conditions, but the game's physics too.<br><br>- 5 special physics presets: <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Speedsters </strong>- Everyone runs even faster.<br></li><li> <strong>Low Gravity </strong>- Both players and balls falls slower, so jumping requires more commitment.<br></li><li> <strong>Grounded </strong>- Jumping is disabled. Master your dashing and parrying skills.<br></li><li> <strong>Fastball </strong>- All throws are faster, even when uncharged.<br></li><li> <strong>On a Dime </strong>- Makes controls tighter, for extra competitive players.<br></li><li> <strong>Custom </strong>- Adjust every physics knob to suit your tastes.</li></ul>",
